    {
      "id": "xlVJXCBeVaY2symJIzTf",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 60,
      "y": 1125,
      "width": 1160,
      "height": 75,
      "text": "• Flying is everyday, but route + weather + atmosphere of a specific flight are invisible afterwards\n• Existing flight trackers (Flightradar24, FlightAware) are 2D dashboards, not cinematic\n• My HW5 Earth shader and HW2/4/6 data pipelines are the natural building blocks",
      "fontSize": 18,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 15,
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "• Flying is everyday, but route + weather + atmosphere of a specific flight are invisible afterwards\n• Existing flight trackers (Flightradar24, FlightAware) are 2D dashboards, not cinematic\n• My HW5 Earth shader and HW2/4/6 data pipelines are the natural building blocks",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "autoResize": true,
