    {
      "id": "UDFC5WsFC0E65PbShort",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 680,
      "y": 5750,
      "width": 520,
      "height": 380,
      "text": "• Live OpenSky / Trino fetch in preprocessor\n• Multi-variable weather: clouds + precip + storms + fog\n• Day / night terminator transition along long flights\n• Multiple cameras: route overview, cinematic, cabin window\n• On-screen HUD (altitude, speed, ETA, timestamp)\n• Seat-side recommendation (sun vs cloud vs view)",
      "fontSize": 18,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 15,
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "• Live OpenSky / Trino fetch in preprocessor\n• Multi-variable weather: clouds + precip + storms + fog\n• Day / night terminator transition along long flights\n• Multiple cameras: route overview, cinematic, cabin window\n• On-screen HUD (altitude, speed, ETA, timestamp)\n• Seat-side recommendation (sun vs cloud vs view)",
