      "y": 6694,
      "width": 524,
      "height": 150,
      "text": "A. ERA5 NetCDF (Copernicus) — global, hourly, since 1940  ← preferred\nB. Open-Meteo Historical API — JSON, simpler, fewer variables\nC. NOAA METAR — aviation-relevant but station-based, sparse",
